snippet.title: Equinox | Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Equinox, EVE Online’s first major expansion for 2024, is live! Seize control and dominate in a re-invigorated nullsec, flying your true colors. Harness the true potential of your sovereign space with new technology and planetary resources, but be prepared to defend against opportunistic foes. Set your sights on new daily goals and corporation projects, fly new ships, and express your creativity and identity with personalized ship SKINs. Get ready to experience enhanced ground combat with adaptive weapons on a brand new map, coming with the Solstice event from 20 June-1 July, in the biggest EVE Vanguard update to date. 

Start playing for free at: https://EVE.Online/Fly_Now 

Seize control: https://www.eveonline.com/now/equinox 

#eveonline #mmo #spacegames #expansion
